{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Immerse yourself in the soothing world of <strong>Block Collide</strong>, a relaxing and visually minimalist puzzle game designed to challenge your brain without overwhelming you. With 50 uniquely crafted puzzles, each offering varying levels of difficulty, <strong>Block Collide</strong> keeps gameplay fresh and rewarding as you solve puzzles by moving cubes to their goals\u2014all while making sure they don\u2019t collide.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">As you progress, new mechanics are introduced, such as cubes that move in pairs, pause nodes that freeze movements, and locks that create new strategic obstacles. Every puzzle is a test of timing and order, ensuring no two levels feel the same. The calming <strong>atmospheric soundtrack</strong>, composed specifically for the game, enhances the experience and helps keep you relaxed as you solve the increasingly tricky puzzles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Block Collide</strong> offers full flexibility in controls\u2014whether you prefer using the <strong>mouse, keyboard, or gamepad</strong>, the choice is yours. Completing each level unlocks an achievement, giving you a satisfying sense of progress.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Key Features</strong>:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>50 Puzzles</strong>: Solve a range of puzzles, from easy to challenging, as you navigate cubes toward their goals without colliding.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Minimalist Art Style</strong>: Enjoy a clean and simple visual experience designed to help you focus on the puzzle-solving.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Relaxing Atmosphere</strong>: Accompanied by a custom-composed <strong>ambient soundtrack</strong> to enhance relaxation and concentration.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Innovative Mechanics</strong>: Encounter new gameplay elements such as paired cubes, pause nodes, and locks to keep the puzzles engaging.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Flexible Controls</strong>: Play how you want\u2014use the <strong>mouse</strong>, <strong>keyboard</strong>, or <strong>gamepad</strong> for an intuitive experience.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Achievements</strong>: Unlock an achievement for every puzzle you complete, motivating you to keep solving.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Whether you're looking for a casual puzzle to relax with or a rewarding mental challenge, <strong>Block Collide</strong> delivers a serene yet engaging gameplay experience.</p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Level 5","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1797250/8ea589acc755fa2a9ce9d295590613bc775ddfbc.jpg"},{"name":"Level 10","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1797250/cc34104f415f355c17786a98afcd4895179e9595.jpg"},{"name":"Level 15","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1797250/932166dffc502c0d9bd737396482f0f134d874ee.jpg"},{"name":"Level 20","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1797250/2bae089db90693a9d8813faf562b901db793343c.jpg"},{"name":"Level 25","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1797250/ce556bbb425de04b7f4282d3b0dddb7459e71abe.jpg"},{"name":"Level 30","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1797250/505efc165eb7aaa9c0c95dd34132548222127baf.jpg"},{"name":"Level 35","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1797250/5d31ef6953f0b6fde2e0f341ea2ff06b88442f1d.jpg"},{"name":"Level 40","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1797250/c6fde301f04fcf5b6a2614eb3fa13b547876b4cb.jpg"},{"name":"Level 45","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1797250/49ec5b72c1764fe40c4ee4ea6943229a0c73ab9d.jpg"},{"name":"Level